nodes.bodyText: Could you clean up the static imports so they are adjacent?
Actually there were several cases of unused imports for JUnit. I used a sed script to make the JUnit changes, so these were there before, but I'll be glad to clean them up.

Looks like this got updated in after the shape change was integrated. @karllessard do you think it's worth making a separate PR (or just you push the ops update separately) so we don't have commits that make unintentional changes?

I think it is up to you @JimClarke5 , normally this file should have been committed in your previous PR adding shape operators. Ideally we would commit it as a separate PR to keep this history clean, but I won't insist neither if you prefer we keep things simpler and just merge this PR as is.
